  stimulus_text = 'The author''s main purpose is to present a comprehensive argument about the importance of protecting cultural heritage. The author begins by describing the challenges faced by many traditional cultures in the modern world. The author then presents several examples of successful efforts to preserve cultural heritage, citing specific examples of how these efforts have benefited the communities involved. The author concludes by offering a call to action, urging readers to support efforts to protect cultural heritage.',
